e-johnson-wants-to-do-more-dramatic-work-on-films-that-matter-3566744">约翰逊表示他打算拍摄更具戏剧性的电影，远离使他成名的动作大片。</a></p><h2><strong>有关心理健康的帮助和建议：</strong></h2><ul><li> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/am-i-depressed-how-to-tell-2067753">“我抑郁吗？” – 有关心理健康以及下一步该做什么的帮助和建议</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="https://www.helpmusicians.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Help Musicians UK – 为音乐家提供全天候心理健康支持和建议</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="http://www.musicsupport.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">音乐支持组织 – 为与酗酒、成瘾或心理健康问题作斗争的音乐家提供帮助和支持</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="http://www.youngminds.org.uk/?gclid=CIuC-9ye69ICFQYo0wodX48KPA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">YOUNG MINDS – 年轻人健康和福祉的代言人</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="https://www.thecalmzone.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CALM——针对年轻人的反对悲惨生活的运动</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="https://public.eagleapi.io/magpie/time-inc/nme/AUTO/link?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.time-to-change.org.uk%2F&amp;referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nme.com%2Fnews%2Fmusic%2Fdream-state-primrose-path-addiction-mental-health-interview-2560278&amp;vars[ipcTags.contentId]=2560278&amp;vars[magpie_data.ga_id]=18801022.1568737667" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">是时候改变了——让我们结束心理健康歧视</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href="http://www.samaritans.org/how-we-can-help-you/contact-us?gclid=CKyDztKf69ICFSIo0wodYjYL5A" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">撒玛利亚人 – 每天 24 小时提供保密支持</a></strong></li></ul><p>道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/dwayne-johnson-shares-jelly-roll-lyric-that-helped-him-through-a-depressive-period-that-really-moved-me-and-touched-me-3813460">恩·强森 (Dwayne Johnson) 分享了帮助他度过抑郁期的 Jelly Roll 歌词：“这真的让我感动，感动了我”，该歌词</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
