https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/diddy-sean-combs-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Diddy">吹牛老爹</a>被指控付钱给狱友使用手机，并精心策划对话和社交媒体帖子，“目的是影响潜在的陪审团”。</p><p>早在九月份，他就<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-arrested-sexual-misconduct-allegations-3794341">在纽约被捕</a>，随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-charged-with-sex-trafficking-racketeering-and-transporting-for-prostitution-3794598">被指控性贩卖、敲诈勒索和运送卖淫</a>，但他对所有指控均表示不认罪。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-denied-bail-in-sex-trafficking-racketeering-case-3794666">后来他提出了 5000 万美元（3840 万英镑）的保释金，但被拒绝保释</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/p-diddy-reportedly-placed-on-suicide-watch-while-awaiting-trial-for-sex-crimes-3795772">据报道，他在等待审判期间被置于自杀监视之下</a>。此后，该艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-appeals-bail-promises-no-women-and-drug-testing-3798498">对保释被拒提出上诉，</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddys-sex-trafficking-trial-date-set-for-2025-3801704">审判日期定于 2025 年 5 月 5 日</a>。</p><p>根据<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/sean-combs-bond-hearing-sex-trafficking-racketeering-jail-1235169449/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>获得的法庭文件，纽约南区检察官指控这位名誉扫地的说唱大亨使用至少八名其他囚犯的电话账户，违反了监狱规定。</p><p>检察官表示，他们有他拨打的各种电话的录音。 </p><figure id="attachment_3804765" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3804765" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3804765" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Diddy@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Sean“Diddy”Combs 将于 2023 年 10 月 20 日在霍华德大学 Yardfest 上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Diddy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Diddy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Diddy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Diddy@20