ets-sell-out-in-just-six-minutes-3434255">在短短六分钟内重新出售门票</a>。上一年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2022-fans-react-as-resale-tickets-sell-out-in-20-minutes-3191018">重新出售的门票售罄</a>。</p><p>对于本周无法获得门票的人， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-2025-tickets-buy-how-to-price-line-up-faq-3809687">通常在春季提供售票</a>。但是，这些往往很快就会卖光，教练和门票重新出售捆绑包<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-as-glastonbury-2024-ticket-and-coach-re-sale-tickets-sell-out-in-18-minutes-3619638">在短短18分钟内就卖光了</a>，今年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-as-final-glastonbury-2024-tickets-sell-out-in-20-minutes-3742591">22分钟内售出了</a>一般的销售票。</p><p> 2024年的音乐节看到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/dua-lipa-live-at-glastonbury-2024-review-setlist-photos-3770003">Dua Lipa</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/coldplay-glastonbury-2024-live-review-photos-setlist-3770486">Coldplay</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/sza-live-at-glastonbury-2024-setlist-review-photos-3770784">Sza</a>头条新闻，还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/shania-twain-glastonbury-2024-setlist-photos-3770685">Shania Twain</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/little-simz-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-stage-setlist-photos-3770489">Little Simz</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/fontaines-dc-live-at-glastonbury-2024-review-setlist-photos-3770000">Fontaines DC</a>和IDLE的其他令人难忘的套装。</p><p> 2025年的阵容仍在包裹中 - 尽管联合组织者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/emily-eavis">艾米丽·埃维斯（Emily Eavis）</a>在今年的节日末证实， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/emily-eavis-confirms-glastonbury-fallow-year-2026-in-talks-with-acts-for-2025-3770919">她已经与某些行为“已经在谈话”</a> - 但<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/glastonbury-2025-headliners-rumours-3773153">在传闻中的头条新闻中，</a>她是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈（Olivia Rodrigo）</a> - 他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-announces-her-biggest-ever-uk-show-at-bst-hyde-park-2025-3811479">在英国6月27日，举办BST Hyde Park标题展览</a>-<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">绿日</a>- 宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/download-2025-announced-stacked-line-up-with-green-day-sleep-token-korn-and-more-tickets-3812026">将于6月初下载标题</a>- <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/acdc">AC/DC</a> 。</p><p>其他提示的包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">哈里·斯泰尔斯（Harry Styles）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">萨姆·芬德（Sam Fender）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">雷（Raye</a> ），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）</a> - 他将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-confirmed-as-second-glastonbury-2020-headliner-2587441">2020年成为2019年大流行前的头条新闻</a>，并导致了节日的取消 - 以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eminem">阿姆（Eminem）</a> 。</p><p>在宣布明年的团圆巡回演出之后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>曾被谣传，但他们确认，明年他们不会与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-on-why-oasis-wont-be-playing-glastonbury-2025-3803430">主持人利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）一起参加节日，上个月在推文中称格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）为“充满滴水”</a> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-tickets-sell-out-in-35-minutes-3813419">格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）2025年：门票在35分钟内售罄，新的排队系统：“你好两个酒吧我的老朋友”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
